The system uses a materials_db.json file to store alloy properties, allowing users to easily add new materials without changing the source code:


content_copy

"1.7225 (42CrMo4)": {
"composition": {"C": [0.38, 0.45], "Cr": [0.9, 1.2]},
"mechanical": {"yield_strength": 650, "tensile_strength": 900}
}

